title: NGO CSW Forum, CSW 60
desc: The NGO Committee on the Status of Women, NY (NGO CSW/NY) organized an NGO CSW Forum. We are requiring that everyone attending the forum registers.?Register for the NGO Forum to receive advance updates and schedules. This year we are offering our members an early bird discount of $10 off both Consultation Day and the Reception!?  between November 16th and November 30th and you will receive your discount code on December 1st.
